sequenceDiagram
    participant Creator as Marketplace creator
    participant Admin as Global marketplace admin
    participant UI as Marketplace UI
    participant API as Analytics API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL marketplace tables
    Creator->>UI: Open creator dashboard
    UI->>API: GET /api/marketplace/creators/{creator_id}/analytics
    API->>DB: Verify creator ownership by user id
    API->>DB: Aggregate installs, purchases, ledger, reviews, reports, package signals
    DB-->>API: Creator product performance
    API-->>UI: Installs, revenue, conversion, errors
    Admin->>UI: Open internal marketplace dashboard
    UI->>API: GET /api/marketplace/analytics/admin
    API->>API: Require global admin or super admin
    API->>DB: Aggregate submissions, approval time, installs, refunds, reports, blocked packages
    DB-->>API: Health and risky-product signals
    API-->>UI: Marketplace health analytics and ranked risk list
